  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Kotlin]]></title>
    <link href="http://knmsyk.github.io/blog/2015-06-03-kotlin.html"/>
    <updated>2015-06-03T22:01:00+09:00</updated>
    <id>http://knmsyk.github.io/blog/kotlin</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>
<a href="http://kotlinlang.org/docs/reference/">Kotlin の公式 Reference</a> を読みながら気になったところをまとめる
</p>

<p>
<!-- more -->
</p>

<div id="outline-container-sec-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-1">Getting stated</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-1-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-1">Basic syntax</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-1">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-1-1-1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-1-1-1">Defining local variables</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-1-1-1">
<p>
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='kotlin'><span class='line'><span class="k">val</span> <span class="py">immutable</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">Int</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="m">1</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="k">var</span> <span class="py">mutable</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">Double</span><span class="p">?</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="m">2</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-sec-2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-2">Basics</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-2">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-2-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-2-1">Basic types</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-1">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><a href="http://kotlinlang.org/docs/reference/basic-types.html">http://kotlinlang.org/docs/reference/basic-types.html</a>
</li>
<li>generics や nullable な number は boxing される
</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-sec-2-2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-2-2">triple quote</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-2">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>raw text を生成する
</li>
</ul>
<p>
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='kotlin'><span class='line'><span class="k">val</span> <span class="py">text</span> <span class="p">=</span> <span class="s">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">for</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">c</span> <span class="k">in</span> <span class="s">&quot;foo&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">c</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="outline-container-sec-2-3" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-2-3">Return and jumps</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-2-3">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-2-3-1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-2-3-1">Break and Continue Labels</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-2-3-1">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Labeling
</li>
</ul>

<p>
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='kotlin'><span class='line'><span class="n">loop</span><span class="err">@</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span> <span class="k">in</span> <span class="m">1.</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="m">100</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">for</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">j</span> <span class="k">in</span> <span class="m">1.</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="m">100</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(&amp;</span><span class="err">#</span><span class="n">x2026</span><span class="p">;)</span>
</span><span class='line'>      <span class="k">break</span><span class="n">@loop</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Automatic labeling
</li>
</ul>
<p>
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='kotlin'><span class='line'><span class="k">fun</span> <span class="nf">foo</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="n">ints</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">forEach</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">it</span> <span class="p">==</span> <span class="m">0</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">return</span><span class="n">@forEach</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="n">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">it</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='kotlin'><span class='line'><span class="k">fun</span> <span class="nf">outer</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="k">fun</span> <span class="nf">inner</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="k">return</span><span class="n">@outer</span> <span class="c1">// the label @outer was defined automatically</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="p">}</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
]]></content>
