<h3 id="sec-4-2">Neuron model: Logistic unit</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-4-2">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Node
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>is a unit of mimicking neuron
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Edge
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>connect to units of next layer
</li>
<li>is mimicking Synapse conection
</li>
<li>Each edge have weight (coefficient)
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><b>Parameter</b>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Layer
<ol class="org-ol">
<li>Input layer
</li>
<li>Hidden layer
</li>
<li>Output layer
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>Activation function of neuron
<ul class="org-ul">
